<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">Welcome to my Project</h1>
<p class="mb-3 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center">In this project I'm practicing the basics of Stimulus, Hotwire, and Tailwind CSS in rails 7!</p>

<h2 class="text-2xl mb-2 font-bold">Example# 1</h2>
<div data-controller="hello">
  <input data-hello-target="name" type="text" placeholder='type any name here'>
  <button data-action="click->hello#greet" type="button" class="outline-none text-white bg-green-700 mx-2 hover:bg-green-800 focus:ring-0 focus:ring-green-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 mr-2 mb-2 dark:bg-green-600 dark:hover:bg-green-700 dark:focus:ring-green-800">Greet</button>
  <span data-hello-target="output" class="text-gray-500"></span>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl my-2 font-bold">Example# 2</h2>
<div data-controller="clipboard" data-clipboard-supported-class="clipboard--supported">
  <input data-clipboard-target="source" type="text" value="7GKL08" readonly>
  <button data-action="click->clipboard#copy" type="button" class="outline-none text-white bg-gray-700 mx-2 hover:bg-gray-800 focus:ring-0 focus:ring-gray-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 mr-2 mb-2 dark:bg-gray-600 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:focus:ring-gray-800">Copy to Clipboard</button>
  <span data-clipboard-target="output" class="text-green-500"><i></i></span>
</div>

<p class="mt-3">Let's apply CRUD operations via Hotwire: </p>
